				\begin{document}$$ \left( {\dot{F}_{\text{s}} } \right) $$\end{document} showed a gradual reduction which might be owing to an increase in bond length or interatomic spacing.Fig. 7
The Poisson’s ratio as a function of packing density (Cg) and the molar volume (Vm) of the BZX glasses
